title: Eddie Has A Problem With Bobby + Reba On Doing A Reunion Of Her Sitcom + Songs We Forgot About Are Jams!
itunes:title: Eddie Has A Problem With Bobby + Reba On Doing A Reunion Of Her Sitcom + Songs We Forgot About Are Jams!
description:
Eddie went over to Bobby’s yesterday to play basketball and now has a problem with something he did. We talk to Reba about the 30th anniversary of her ‘Rumor Has It” album, how she got her signature hair and if she’d do a reunion of her television show. Plus, we each share songs we forgot about that were jams from back in the day!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
